eu.liveandgov.wp1.human_activity_recognition.helper

Class TimedQueue<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.liveandgov.wp1.human_activity_recognition.helper.TimedQueue<V>

  • public class TimedQueue<V>
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that holds samples in a time frame of a given duration d. The time frame ends with the time stamp t of the last sample that was pushed to the queue and starts after the time t - d (exclusively). Time ---(t-d)--------t--> Samples: + + | + + + + + + | Last Sample in queue Contents of Queue: + + + + + + Removed samples: + + Created by cehlen, hartmann on 10/18/13.
